were bestowed by His Majesty.

125
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:46,360
(He has no reaction.)

126
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,560
(Can't humiliating him in this way)

127
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,839
(arouse his hatred?)

128
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:20,879
Shu,

129
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,120
