131
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,519
This is Carefree Powder.

132
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,079
Colorless and tasteless.

133
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,160
It can erase one's internal strength,

134
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,480
causing a sudden death

135
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,279
without being detected.

136
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:35,919
And this.
A blood-red agate jade bracelet.

137
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,840
My people managed

138
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,000
to find it from Zhuyan State.

139
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,639
Its color is as pure

140
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,440
