149
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:08,440
It's bad.

150
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:12,159
His Majesty accused us of rebellion
and sent the Shadow Guards to kill us.

151
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,480
Si Sheng has betrayed us
and opened the city gate.

152
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,919
